- Fallback 2: `anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5`

## Qdrant Collections
- `synapse_knowledge` — document RAG vectors
- `synapse_memory` — mem0 user memory vectors

## Security
- Tenant BYOK keys → Fernet AES-256 encrypted in PostgreSQL
- All API keys → `os.environ["KEY_NAME"]`
- tenant_id payload filter on EVERY Qdrant query
